name: INDIAN LOVE - WALL BANNER
description:
INDIAN LOVE - WALL BANNER
The Indian Love illustrations has been my most popular print to date!
It is the piece Little Quarters is best known for and identified by.

This Wall Banner is available as a beautiful Limited Edition Print, as well as this stunning Wall Banner at 60 x 70cm this piece is ready for hanging, in your beautiful home.

With just the slight hint of colour this piece will suit most decors.

LIMITED EDITION and MADE TO ORDER.
Designed and Illustrated by Little Quarters.
Lovingly hand sewn and locally printed in Melbourne, Australia. 

75% linen 25% cotton with raw rope and black pom pom detail.

PLEASE NOTE: These pieces are made to order so can take up to 2 weeks from purchase date if I do not have any ready to go in my studio. 
These guys are shipped safe and sound in a custom Little Quarters postal tube. 
Each print is unique, and slight variations are to be embraced.

Whole Sale Inquiries are welcome - littlequarters@gmail.com

©Little Quarters by Sarah Pook 2013.
